342 & 4.91 & 48 & 39 & High-frequency option \\
\rowcolor{shaderow} 99 & 4.76 & 52 & 38 & Frequent mid-sequence \\
267 & 4.61 & 43 & 36 & \\
\rowcolor{shaderow} 88 & 4.44 & 39 & 33 & \\
